&lt;Bando McGlocklin CapitalCorp> said it filed a registration statement with theSecurities and Exchange Commission coverig a proposed initialpublic offering of 750,000 shares of common stock.    The closed end investment company estimated the offering'sprice at between seven dlr and eight dlrs a share.    The company said it is selling all the shares under theunderwriting group management of The Milwaukee Co.    Bando said it will use the net proceeds to repay loans andreduce debt. Reuter&#3;